#EXTM3U
# Your own open-internet channels. iptv-org already covers the common BD
# channels (it's a source in manifest.json and auto-updates), so only add
# channels it lacks here — or override one by reusing the same channel name.
#
# Two lines per channel:
#   #EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="LOGO_URL" group-title="CATEGORY",Channel Name
#   STREAM_URL
